title: SC EP:225 Sasquatch Vocalizations
itunes:title: SC EP:225 Sasquatch Vocalizations
description: Randy Harrington will be stopping by to share his recent audio he captured while in Washington State. We will review his audio and he will be sharing with us how he captured the audio and what was going on while he was recording. Randy will also be sharing with us a recent encounter he looked into of a woman claiming she has Sasquatch on her property. Very strange story, you will not want to miss it.
